                                        <Bold>WolvenKit</Bold>
                                        <LineBreak />
                                        <LineBreak />
                                        This program is being created to extend mod support for games made by CD Projekt Red on their proprietary REDEngine, namely The Witcher 3 and Cyberpunk 2077.<LineBreak />
                                        <LineBreak />
                                        As the tool is being made fully for educational purposes, the authors are in no way responsible of complications regarding your PC or your game installation(s).<LineBreak />
                                        <LineBreak />
                                        This project is completely open source, open to contribution and in no way made with the aim of generating revenue.<LineBreak />
                                        <LineBreak />
                                        The precursor to this project, W3Edit, was developed by Sarcenzzz in 2015 when the game originally came out.<LineBreak />
                                        <LineBreak />
                                        Upon him eventually abandoning it, a few of us modders decided to continue it.<LineBreak />
                                        <LineBreak />
                                        Currently, the reading/writing of nearly every REDEngine file format is possible to some extent.<LineBreak />
                                        <LineBreak />
                                        It goes without saying that this is a work in progress, so do make sure to check on its status regularly.<LineBreak />
                                        <LineBreak />
                                        Our current primary focus is advancing support for the new game, Cyberpunk 2077.</Paragraph>
                                </FlowDocument>
                            </FlowDocumentPageViewer>
